edu.stanford.nlp.trees

Class EnglishPatterns

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.stanford.nlp.trees.EnglishPatterns

  • public class EnglishPatterns
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains some English String or Tregex regular expression patterns. They originated in other classes like EnglishGrammaticalRelations, but were collected here so that they could be used without having to load large classes (which we might want to have parallel versions of. Some are just stored here as String objects, since they are often used as sub-patterns inside larger patterns.
    Author:
    Christopher Manning
